Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的月色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.62,0:00:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.66,0:00:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，有流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.06,0:00:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快許個願吧\N- 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳許了什麼願呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.70,0:00:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘. 密.\N史派克呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?當然是秘密啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.26,0:00:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧，史派克?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小事不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.00,0:01:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說我可是見習騎士哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮絲，我的願望是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士把劍弄丟了就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大劍!\N(音同"大騷動"，不得了的意思)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大騷動、大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還滿有兩下子的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到大大的高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.55,0:01:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.52,0:01:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下跑出來做什麼的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.59,0:01:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然跑到附近來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.86,0:01:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是表情看起來不像在這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.79,0:01:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，這次一定要牽到手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.92,0:01:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是叔叔呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊潘恩!我跟你道歉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊，伯伯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆!我才不是什麼伯伯呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一個接著一個來搗蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.17,0:01:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，史派克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝…\N- 哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，有沒有受傷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上用魔法幫你治療\N快到亮一點的地方來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.55,0:01:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.02,0:01:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多說快點來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.85,0:01:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YA!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
